text:
Mats are very good quality and iam very inpressed with them and fit perfectly the only thing is my Fiesta as not got the safety fittings?? built into the carpet so iam left with two holes in the mat but still looks good though.
Wish Car Mats UK did boot carpets!
Regards Steve
